arStrings.szText: Normally, I'd have done this sorta thing m'self, but I'll walk barefoot into the Burning Hells 'fore I go wanderin' the coast alone.
Wants to assert she's generally self-sufficient, but she's also not stupid enough to ignore the danger around here
The Drowned out here are nasty creatures, and I ain't lookin' to join their ranks.
Emphasis on nasty; she doesn't want anything to do with them
